    <item>
      <title>中国要求经纪商限制“滚雪球”衍生品的风险敞口</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/china-tells-brokers-to-limit-exposure-to-snowball-derivatives</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在券商将回报率提高至接近历史最高水平以吸引投资者购买股市抛售后的高风险产品后，中国正在采取行动遏制“滚雪球”衍生品。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/china-tells-brokers-to-limit-exposure-to-snowball-derivatives</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 09:14:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞安航空首席执行官敦促波音公司在危机期间保持领导力连续性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/ryanair-ceo-urges-leadership-continuity-at-boeing-during-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞安航空控股公司首席执行官迈克尔·奥利里表示，波音公司管理层在寻求稳定业务的过程中需要关注连续性，商用飞机部门的新负责人已经取得了良好的开端。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/ryanair-ceo-urges-leadership-continuity-at-boeing-during-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 09:08:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Investcorp 设立由中国中投公司支持的 10 亿美元中东基金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/investcorp-sets-up-1-billion-mideast-fund-backed-by-china-s-cic</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中东最大的另类资产管理公司正在建立一个由北京主权财富基金支持的 10 亿美元投资工具，投资波斯湾和中国的公司。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/investcorp-sets-up-1-billion-mideast-fund-backed-by-china-s-cic</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 08:59:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>汇丰银行分析师表示，Gucci 的扭亏为盈需要更多时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-24/gucci-turnaround-will-take-more-time-hsbc-analyst-says-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[汇丰银行奢侈品和体育用品分析师 Aurelie Husson-Dumoutier 表示，开云集团扭转 Gucci 局面的尝试将比预期花费更长的时间。她在彭博电视台发表讲话时解释说，虽然美国已经进入了更加正常化的增长道路，但这“不足以弥补中国消费者的疲软”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-04-24/gucci-turnaround-will-take-more-time-hsbc-analyst-says-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 08:43:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞银董事长称瑞士资本计划是“错误的补救措施”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/ubs-chairman-says-he-s-seriously-concerned-over-capital-reforms</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞银集团董事长科尔姆·凯莱赫表示，瑞士政府要求该银行持有更多资本的提议是针对一年多前导致瑞士信贷垮台的“错误补救措施”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/ubs-chairman-says-he-s-seriously-concerned-over-capital-reforms</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 08:36:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Gucci 暴跌引发盈利警告后开云集团股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/kering-shares-drop-after-gucci-slump-prompts-profit-warning</link>
      <description><![CDATA[开云集团警告称，由于其最大品牌古驰 (Gucci) 销售额下滑，今年上半年利润将大幅下降，开云集团股价应声暴跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/kering-shares-drop-after-gucci-slump-prompts-profit-warning</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 24 Apr 2024 07:10:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球最大的能源贸易商正在回归金属</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/world-s-biggest-energy-traders-are-returning-to-metals-markets</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界上一些最大的能源贸易公司在众所周知的困难市场中遭受损失多年后，正在重返金属领域。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-24/world-s-biggest-energy-traders-are-returning-to-metals-markets</guid>
